FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1778105470
OL,3,CExperts discover potential cause for
OL,4,Cstroke affecting 35,000 people in the
OL,5,CUK
OL,7,FUnlike ischaemic strokes, which are
OL,8,Fcaused by a blocked blood vessel,
OL,9,Fexperts at the University of Edinburgh
OL,10,Fand the UK Dementia Research Institute
OL,11,Fsuggest lacunar strokes may be caused
OL,12,Fby the widening of arteries in the
OL,13,Fbrain.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1778105470
OL,3,CExperts discover potential cause for
OL,4,Cstroke affecting 35,000 people in the
OL,5,CUK
OL,7,FThe study included 229 people who had
OL,8,Fexperienced a lacunar or mild non-
OL,9,Flacunar stroke. They underwent
OL,10,Fcognitive tests and brain scans at the
OL,11,Ftime of the stroke and again one year
OL,12,Flater. Researchers tracked the cause
OL,13,Fof the stroke, signs of small vessel
OL,14,Fdisease and new areas of brain damage.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1778105470
OL,3,CExperts discover potential cause for
OL,4,Cstroke affecting 35,000 people in the
OL,5,CUK
OL,7,FThe analysis found that the narrowing
OL,8,Fof large arteries was not linked to
OL,9,Flacunar stroke, but rather the
OL,10,Fwidening of arteries. Patients with
OL,11,Fwidened arteries were four times more
OL,12,Flikely to have a lacunar stroke,
OL,13,Faccording to the study.
OL,15,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,16,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,17,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,18,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
