PN,31608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1778105470
OL,3,CExperts discover potential cause for
OL,4,Cstroke affecting 35,000 people in the
OL,5,CUK
OL,7,F"Recognising this distinction is
OL,8,Fcrucial, because it explains why
OL,9,Fconventional treatments like anti-
OL,10,Fplatelet drugs are not as effective
OL,11,Ffor this type of stroke and highlights
OL,12,Fthe urgent need to develop new
OL,13,Ftherapies that target the underlying
OL,14,Fmicrovascular damage."
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@VO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
