CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1778105470
OL,3,CExperts discover potential cause for
OL,4,Cstroke affecting 35,000 people in the
OL,5,CUK
OL,7,FThe findings, published in the journal
OL,8,FCirculation, are being used in studies
OL,9,Fexploring lacunar stroke treatments,
OL,10,Fincluding the LACunar Intervention
OL,11,FTrial 3 (LACI-3), which is testing if
OL,12,Fexisting drugs are effective against
OL,13,Fthe condition.
